fields.title: Zack is awesome!
fields.text: Zach has been helping me with a final project for my Python class, where we are using Django. He is very knowledgeable on the subject, and will also meet you wherever you are at in the learning process. Overall, he is amiable, patient, and adaptable, so I would definitely recommend him if you need help!
